Insurance Analytics Dashboard (Excel)
This repository contains an interactive Excel dashboard created for analyzing insurance data. The dashboard visualizes key performance indicators (KPIs) that help in understanding business trends and decision-making.

## Dashboard Features

- Total policies in the system, both active and inactive
- Total customers holding one or more policies
- Gender-wise policy count to analyze adoption trends
- Breakdown of policies by policy type
- Policies set to expire in the current calendar year for renewal tracking
- Premium revenue growth rate over time
- Claim status summary (approved, rejected, pending)
- Payment status overview (paid, overdue, pending)
- Total claim amount paid out

**Microsoft Excel**
Tools:
  - Pivot Tables
  - Charts & Graphs
  - Slicers and Interactivity
  - Conditional Formatting
